  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Glimpse\" takes you on a journey through the mind of a man haunted by the erosion of his mind. As you traverse a labyrinth of distorted reality, you'll witness the internal fears and confusion faced by those with Alzheimer's disease.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683490/extras/ebd11d59e5023d5c5bb54ee94c5994ec.poster.avif?t=1765935902\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683490/extras/ebd11d59e5023d5c5bb54ee94c5994ec.webm?t=1765935902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683490/extras/ebd11d59e5023d5c5bb54ee94c5994ec.mp4?t=1765935902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A confusing and unsettling experience. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level has a distinct look and atmosphere. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dialogues and an interactable environment.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683490/extras/253391d69981ca722fe3e671755b348c.poster.avif?t=1765935902\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683490/extras/253391d69981ca722fe3e671755b348c.webm?t=1765935902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683490/extras/253391d69981ca722fe3e671755b348c.mp4?t=1765935902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>IMPORTANT: </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This game doesn't save your progress and is meant to be played in one sitting. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Average playtime: ~20 minutes.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683490/extras/3de86ef7b4b2aa819bc4ef683be269a2.poster.avif?t=1765935902\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683490/extras/3de86ef7b4b2aa819bc4ef683be269a2.webm?t=1765935902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2683490/extras/3de86ef7b4b2aa819bc4ef683be269a2.mp4?t=1765935902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
